data.description: Decatur Historic District: Charming two-story home built in 1920. Large inviting front porch. The genuine hardwood floors throughout the living areas demonstrate the quality in homes from the early 20th century. Generously proportioned rooms filled with timeless charm await your personal touch. Floor plan is conducive to entertaining. The downstairs master, 4 upstairs bedrooms and 2.5 total baths mean you can live comfortably while having room for children and/or hosting overnight guests. Full unfinished basement provides voluminous storage. This home isn't just a place to live; it's a bridge between the era of the 1920's and the exciting world of today. Sold "as is" with no known defects.
